  1610→COMPOSITE SCORE: ${compositeScore}%
  1611→CATEGORY BREAKDOWN:
  1612→${Object.entries(categoryScores).map(([cat, s]) => `- ${cat}: ${s.score}% (${s.earned}/${s.total} points)`).join('\n')}
  1613→
  1614→DETAILED RESULTS:
  1615→${Object.entries(categoryGroups).map(([cat, data]) =>
  1616→  data.questions.map(q => `[${cat}] Q: ${q.text.substring(0, 100)}... → Score: ${q.score}/${q.maxPoints}${q.aiScore ? ' | ' + (q.aiScore.feedback || '') : ''}`).join('\n')
  1617→).join('\n')}
  1618→
  1619→Provide a recruiter-facing assessment summary.
  1620→
  1621→Return ONLY valid JSON:
